column5: GSAT this weird action right now
GSAT once this goes to 050 again it will bounce fast Dont miss it

GSAT this is setting up nicelyfor JM JM the exceo of gsat lent gsat money through thermo at a high rate 12 Since then he has been using equity markets to pay himself interest on his loan plus a salary for being ceo The last time he can take money from equity markets to pay himself cash is the end of this year Once that ATM dries up he will force gsat into bankruptcy Being the senior lender on the debt he will recoup most of his assets Gsat was never meant to be a real company just a front for JM to collect easy cash I feel bad for the new ceo who has to pretend like he has a real job for JMs sham organization
